title: Bihar CM Nitish Kumar attacked by man during a function in Bakhtiyarpur - Times of India
content: Bihar CM Nitish Kumar attacked by man during a function in Bakhtiyarpur  Times of IndiaView Full coverage on Google News
description: In a major security lapse, Bihar CM Nitish Kumar was attacked by a person while he was attending a function in Bakhtiyarpur. The man was immediately rounded over by security personnel and is being interrogated. Nitish Kumar was in Bakhtiyarpur to pay tribute to noted freedom fighter Shilbhadra Yaji.
